## Technical Validation

### CSS Changes
Modified [system.css](file:///g:/My%20Drive/RoboLedger%20-%20NEW/src/ui/enterprise/system.css) to override Tabulator's default header and cell styling:
```css
.tabulator-header {
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #f87171, #fb923c, #facc15, #4ade80, #60a5fa, #818cf8, #a78bfa) !important;
}
.tabulator-cell {
    font-weight: 400 !important;
}
```

### JS Changes
Updated [app.js](file:///g:/My%20Drive/RoboLedger%20-%20NEW/src/ui/enterprise/app.js) to include `headerSort: true` in column definitions and refactored the switcher pill rendering loop with deduplication.

